summary: My dudes, I haven't tried to write anything for over a year, and here I am, after frantically typing out some dialogue on my...
body:
My dudes, I haven’t tried to write anything for over a year, and here I am, after frantically typing out some dialogue on my phone’s memo app on the wrong side of 3am, looking at it in the light of day and going,

‘Shit, I need to find out how long it’d take to get from Kings Landing to Winterfell if you were a lone rider, who is hiding from pursuers, and hope that its somehow faster than getting there by taking a boat from Dragonstone. God damn it Jaime’
